<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>You have been invited by <%= @question.election.user.pretty_name %> to vote in an election at WeVoteHere.com!</h1>

    <p>You will use your Secret Voting Code (SVC) to securely vote on this question. Even we do not know your secret voting code; once this email is sent, we delete the association from our memory. Therefore, please don't lose your SVC!</p>

    <p>Your SVC is <%= link_to @svc, vote_path(@svc) %>. You can click it to vote.</p>

    <p>You can also view the status of your vote here: <%= link_to "Status", status_vote_path(@svc) %></p>

    <h2>Question Information</h2>
    Owner:
  	<%= link_to @question.election.user.pretty_name, @question.election.user %>
  	<br>
	Election:
  	<%= link_to @question.election.name, @question.election %>
  	<br>
	Question:
  	<%= link_to @question.name, @question %>
 	<br>
 	<br>

	<% unless @question.election.info.blank? %>
	Voting instructions: <%= @question.election.info %>
  	<% end %>

	<br>
	
	<h3>Choices</h3>
	<% @question.choices.each do |choice| %>
		<%= choice.name %>
		<br>
	<% end %>
  </body>
</html>